'''Mónica Susana López de Zetzsche''' is an Argentine engineer.<ref name="cv">{{cite web|url=http://www.ywca.org.ar/mz-cv.htm|title=CV of Mónica Zetzsche|accessdate=1 Dec 2012|publisher=[[YWCA]]}}</ref>
==Biography== Zetzsche studied Engineering at the [[University of Buenos Aires]].<ref name="cv"/>
Since 1992 she presides López Castro SRL.<ref name="cv"/>
She has been President of [[YWCA]] (2003-2007).<ref name="cv"/>
